text: Wang Shian-ming (born 8 September 1940) is a Taiwanese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Taiwan Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
